title: Missing: Beyond The Vanishing Triangle
overview: In 1993, Annie McCarrick disappears without a trace from her Dublin home. 30 years later, her case remains unsolved. A recent upgrade of the case to murder gives her family renewed hope. But might vital clues have been missed? A two-part true-crime series looking at some of the most notorious cases of women who disappeared within a so-called Vanishing Triangle throughout the 1990's.
